ChangeLog

v1.0.0
- Do not expose user's email, use glFusion mail link instead.
- Modifed style to use the core glFusion styles, this allows improved
  integration into other themes.

v0.8.3
------
- Fixed userlist building to only pull users who are authorized to use the
  PM plugin.
- Fixed several E_ALL warning messages
- Improved variable filtering to ensure no monkey business (XSS type stuff)